GetEmail Overview
edit

What is GetEmail?

GetEmail.io uses Big Data & Artificial Intelligence to guess the professional email address of anyone on Earth. GetEmail.io offers 2 Google Chrome Extensions, one for LinkedIn, and another one for Gmail/Outlook/Salesforce, which embed the "email finding" feature in these common interfaces, for a seamless user experience.

Jun 17, 2022(Original Jun 16, 2020)

"Save time hunting for or guessing email addresses"

What do you like best about GetEmail?

Rather than hunting around or guessing email addresses you can save time by clicking a buttion on a LinkedIn profile. Review collected by and hosted on G2.com.

What do you dislike about GetEmail?

Sometimes a personal email address or an out-of-date email connected to a former employer is generated but this still uses up a credit and other than reporting a bug there's no way to flag this up for corrective action to be taken.

Quite a lot of the time I get a message "Sorry email not found" after the system has tried several possibilities. It would be great if the algorithm could be improved to reduce the number of times this happens and provide a working email address more of the time. Review collected by and hosted on G2.com.

Recommendations to others considering GetEmail:

Try the initial free credits before taking out a paid subscription to see if it works for you Review collected by and hosted on G2.com.

What problems is GetEmail solving and how is that benefiting you?

Connecting quickly to potential new clients. Review collected by and hosted on G2.com.
